{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"272bc233-eaea-4977-8320-0954f6acd165","content":"Your `.testsettings` file is a legacy format that's **not supported by modern MSTest/VSTest**. You need to migrate it to a `.runsettings` file. Here's what your file configures and how each setting maps:\n\n| `.testsettings` Setting | `.runsettings` Equivalent |\n|---|---|\n| `TestTimeout = 30000` | `<TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>` in `<MSTest>` |\n| Assembly resolution | Not needed — modern MSTest resolves from build output |\n| Code Coverage collector | `<DataCollector>` in `<DataCollectionRunSettings>` |\n\nLet me create the replacement `.runsettings` file:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_017JkY4Wk3iCj8KLDCuFTPM6","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Creating runsettings migration"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01G2ZqwMnqHyQRDA2PMWob8N","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-c4badd5fd3dc46deb5e711d5492dcd1e/local.runsettings","file_text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>\n  </MSTest>\n  <DataCollectionRunSettings>\n    <DataCollectors>\n      <DataCollector friendlyName=\"Code Coverage\"\n                     uri=\"datacollector://Microsoft/CodeCoverage/2.0\"\n                     assemblyQualifiedName=\"Microsoft.VisualStudio.Coverage.DynamicCoverageDataCollector, Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b03f5f7f11d50a3a\">\n        <Configuration>\n          <CodeCoverage>\n            <ModulePaths>\n              <Exclude>\n                <ModulePath>.*tests\\.dll$</ModulePath>\n              </Exclude>\n            </ModulePaths>\n          </CodeCoverage>\n        </Configuration>\n      </DataCollector>\n    </DataCollectors>\n  </DataCollectionRunSettings>\n</RunSettings>\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-c4badd5fd3dc46deb5e711d5492dcd1e/local.runsettings."}],"interactionId":"5324068d-5710-4f68-8621-c677e1695468","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has an MSTest v3 project with a `.testsettings` file. The `.testsettings` format is legacy and not supported by modern MSTest/VSTest. They need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file. Let me invoke the MSTest migration skill for guidance, but actually I know enough to help directly.\n\nThe `.testsettings` file contains:\n1. Assembly resolution / deployment settings\n2. A test timeout of 30000ms\n3. A code coverage data collector\n\nI should create a `.runsettings` file that replaces this, and update the `.csproj` to reference it.\n\n\nI'll use the migration skill to guide the conversion from `.testsettings` to `.runsettings` format.","outputTokens":761,"requestId":"6802:38B891:3060156:3583E63:69FD4ED7"},"id":"b391ca78-3245-4e39-beb1-eea773ddc49e","timestamp":"2026-05-08T02:48:08.624Z","parentId":"f802cceb-c711-412e-bc12-a5680df8cc83"}
